-- Fidelity's Sweeney Discusses Retirement Income (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-31T16:15:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-31/fidelity-s-sweeney-discusses-retirement-income-audio-.html
John Sweeney, head of planning and 
advisory services at Fidelity Investments in Boston, says that 
retirees should focus on creating income from accounts that are 
taxable. Sweeney talks with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie
Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage" live from the 
Langham Hotel in Boston. They are also joined by guest host 
Peggy Collins.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 11:01
 